These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-1::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, chess, snooker
1. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |  3   |
| Game   | snooker | chess | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-2::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, go, poker
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3   |
| Game   | poker | backgammon | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | drawing | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, mexican, chinese
1. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
2. the malaysian is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |
| Nationality   | chinese | malaysian | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, videographer, chef
1. the chef is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
2. the dancer is between the chef and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |   2    |   3    |
| Job   | chef | dancer | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-6::.
There 3 different types of food: papaya, spinach, lemon
1. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
2. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
3. the person eating spinach is between the person eating papaya and the person eating lemon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |   3   |
| Food   | lemon | spinach | papaya |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-7::.
