.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-5-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, punk
1. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the fan of blues##5
2. the fan of punk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | blues | punk |

